{"tid":842503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒爆料：大陸政府將對范冰冰處分「素顏之刑」","createTime":"2018-09-30T11:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T17:58:24.000Z","uid":53060,"like":161,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"9af661e489a019542f97566f831c33787ae7e826","tid":842503,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"大陸女星范冰冰深陷陰陽合同風暴，迄今下落不明已超過百日，讓外界相當焦急，日本「News postseven」網站表示，范冰冰在大陸是家喻戶曉的超級大明星，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>外貌屬於冷艷美人，不同於日本一貫可愛親民的女星風格</strong></span>，另外也提及范冰冰收入遠勝過一般日本明星。日媒更分析指出，大陸政府可能會對范冰冰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">施以「素顏之刑」</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n日媒大膽預言，表示當年大陸女星劉曉慶先前因為逃漏稅被逮時，被迫素顏公開面對媒體致歉，范冰冰可能也會遭受同樣待遇。由於范冰冰逃稅一案引起極大風波，對致力反貪腐的大陸政府是極佳箭靶，不過也有人猜測這可能只是日媒的猜測而已，目前大陸官方媒體也未對此作出評論，接下來仍是未知數。<br />\n<br />\n對此<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>知情人士私下大表贊同，表示：「越是上流社會的人，越會對此感到巨大羞辱」</strong></span>，不過也有人認為范冰冰會遭受「素顏之刑」純為日媒揣測。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180930001201-260404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180930001201-260404&d=fDVrsvPobmzEZ9WNWW4ClDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=78453129\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180930001201-260404</a>"},{"pid":"2c60780c331749acb2f15df58eebe7c4fc8b2ef7","tid":842503,"uid":53060,"like":192,"dislike":8,"score":184,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/201809242237227081_08463.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F201809242237227081_08463.jpeg&h=c83cbdc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-09-30/656/20180930001210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-09-30%2F656%2F20180930001210.jpg&h=f53722c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日媒爆料范冰冰恐面臨「素顏之刑」。(圖/范冰冰微博)"},{"pid":"762ab1a6abcdfe22af2fe48b32f69874cf3d6b25","tid":842503,"uid":37528,"like":551,"dislike":6,"score":545,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:21:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會認唔到佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a00eb8384579809354a5ca8a2d6a35d193496e","tid":842503,"uid":29804,"like":439,"dislike":6,"score":433,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"全祼道歉"},{"pid":"40e9d31c136b926fb779f0af92b7c66ec59b3cce","tid":842503,"uid":141151,"like":329,"dislike":3,"score":326,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係迫佢素顏上電視？"},{"pid":"2df2de717a41d43a2ec2aa846c624c4cd97ca762","tid":842503,"uid":40226,"like":378,"dislike":1,"score":377,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"屌講到好似生不如死咁"},{"pid":"d27ec097ac416f0cbfc06c8163c56ccde3c2fb22","tid":842503,"uid":72735,"like":21,"dislike":6,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:23:29.000Z","msg":"會唔會好似日本咁要剃頭認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba834a24c261f7d8a83b05d4d74e3fcbdf12a30e","tid":842503,"uid":37528,"like":249,"dislike":3,"score":246,"quote":{"pid":"2df2de717a41d43a2ec2aa846c624c4cd97ca762","tid":842503,"uid":40226,"like":378,"dislike":1,"score":377,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"屌講到好似生不如死咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"可能係比想像更恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd57efccaf1ceb909dceca1fafabe88cc74df472","tid":842503,"uid":52006,"like":292,"dislike":1,"score":291,"quote":{"pid":"ba834a24c261f7d8a83b05d4d74e3fcbdf12a30e","tid":842503,"ui